
Running terminalizer, assuming installed without root:

  export ELECTRON_DISABLE_SANDBOX=true
  npx terminalizer record demo -k -c ./config.yml
  npx terminalizer render demo

Commands for the dataset download demo:

  import hdfstream
  flamingo = hdfstream.open("cosma", "/FLAMINGO")
  snap = flamingo["L1_m10/L1_m10/snapshots/flamingo_0077/flamingo_0077.hdf5"]
  bh_pos = snap["PartType5/Coordinates"][...]
